the driller killer is a 1979 black comedy horror film directed by and starring abel ferrara , carolyn marz , baybi day , and harry schultz .   the plot concerns reno miller , a struggling artist in new york city , turning insane from stress and killing derelicts with a power drill .   the film was infamous for being on the list of " video nasties " in the united kingdom , resulting the film banned from 1984 ( due to new censorship laws ) until 1999 , when a cut version was approved for an 18 ( years of age ) certificate .   the full uncut version was finally passed by the bbfc in november 2002 .   on 10 june 2010 it was re-released as video on demand ( vod ) .